[566.30515, "o", "Trying to fit: R = a + b*u + c*u^2\r\n"]
[566.305666, "o", "\r\nR channel:\r\n"]
[566.306438, "o", "  x=  0, u=-1.000, R=159\r\n  x=200, u=-0.500, R=151\r\n"]
[566.306628, "o", "  x=400, u= 0.000, R=146\r\n  x=600, u= 0.500, R=151\r\n"]
[566.307352, "o", "  x=799, u= 0.998, R=159\r\n\r\nG channel:\r\n  x=  0, u=-1.000, G=197\r\n"]
[566.307402, "o", "  x=200, u=-0.500, G=193\r\n  x=400, u= 0.000, G=190\r\n  x=600, u= 0.500, G=193\r\n  x=799, u= 0.998, G=197\r\n\r\nManual analysis:\r\nR seems linear in u: R(u=0)=150, R(u=-1)=165, R(u=1)=165\r\nThis looks like R = 150 + 15*|u| (symmetric around u=0)\r\n\r\nG seems to increase with u: G(u=-1)=145, G(u=1)~215\r\nG(u=0)=180, so G might be: 145 + 35*u or similar\r\n"]
